{"tid":1393020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一返到公司就眼濕濕 邊個巴絲做好自首啦","createTime":"2019-08-01T02:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:47:30.000Z","uid":258253,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22fe8a9066d7e8769afe6212a84a45b7077226ce","tid":1393020,"uid":258253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"我係香港人<br />\n82我會去<br />\n85齊罷工!<br />\n<br />\n我部門成層好少人支持反送中 <br />\n唔知係支持既人唔出聲 定真係無<br />\n次次去印影同pantry都只會聽到啲同事責怪而家行出黎抗爭既人個個星期搞事<br />\n連721之後果日 做野都無心情既時候<br />\n竟然聽到啲人講笑既語氣講反元朗單野<br />\n重讚班黑警戰術高<br />\n我自問係政府小薯 平時唔敢出聲<br />\n好多謝琴晚3點都重send緊email比我地既巴絲<br />\n第一次係公司見到咁正面既野<br />\n希望你地既email可以喚醒其他同事<br />\n真係好多謝你地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOtXUNu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOtXUNu.png&h=7010d6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYchULv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYchULv.png&h=239bbff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7vjoDR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7vjoDR.png&h=ebab80cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaUDEcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaUDEcb.png&h=3fe11af2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"404f08c639af645202f73f56f160d0d116d38d69","tid":1393020,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff12e64b13043738c7270a170d9eb0d12fff500","tid":1393020,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2174c57cd85fa98cac9be2e358b7fc8e7a91cf","tid":1393020,"uid"